02:01.589 --> 02:03.522
Uh...

02:03.524 --> 02:04.790
Oh...

02:04.792 --> 02:07.493
I'm sorry. I thought
I heard... Singing.

02:07.495 --> 02:09.294
<i>¶ I'm a little lamb</i>

02:09.296 --> 02:12.397
<i>¶ who's lost in the woods</i>

02:12.399 --> 02:14.133
<i>¶ I know I could</i>

02:14.135 --> 02:16.535
<i>¶ could always be good</i>

02:16.537 --> 02:17.903
<i>¶ to one who'll watch</i>

02:17.905 --> 02:19.538
Must've been
out in the hallway.

02:19.540 --> 02:20.806
<i>¶ over me</i>

02:20.808 --> 02:22.741
I-I'm sorry to disturb you.

02:22.743 --> 02:25.911
Mr. Adams was
