02:27.413 --> 02:29.815
Dr. Harris?
<i>¶ won't you tell her please</i>

02:29.817 --> 02:32.551
<i>¶ to put on some speed?</i>
<i>We'll come back later</i>
<i>and check on your husband.</i>

02:32.553 --> 02:34.586
<i>¶ follow my lead</i>

02:34.588 --> 02:36.822
<i>¶ oh, how I need</i>

02:36.824 --> 02:40.459
Oliver adams, 35.
<i>¶ someone to watch</i>

